Degtyarev surprised by information about the purchase of gas "Sakhalin-1" for dollars
Interim Governor of the Khabarovsk Territory Mikhail Degtyarev on Sunday, July 26, during a meeting with residents of Soviet Havana was surprised that the region buys Sakhalin gas, mined by the American company Exxon Neftegas, for dollars.
US gas is contracted in dollars until 2025.
“I honestly didn’t know, and I’m in such a knockdown because of this information.
I had no idea that this was still possible in Russia in 2020,” he told RIA Novosti.
