Singer Polina Gagarina called the products that help to lose weight
Russian singer Polina Gagarina named five products that helped her correct the figure and subsequently not gain weight again.
The first on the list was water.
The singer prefers to drink clean non-carbonated water before each meal to dull the feeling of hunger and eat less.
Vegetable salad, brown rice and seafood are also ideal for maintaining slenderness.
Thanks to them, you can make a balanced diet: vegetables contain fiber, rice has complex carbohydrates, and seafood is a source of protein, useful vitamins and amino acids.
For the unloading days, the singer chooses apples.
Thanks to these products, Gagarina was able to get rid of 30 extra pounds.
In addition, the singer switched to a fractional diet - she eats often and gradually and excluded from the diet fat, sweet and caloric.
Gagarin does not eat fried food, baked goods, sausages and other meat semi-finished products, writes kp.ru July 26.
It also replaced fish and seafood with red meat.
Prefers vegetables (except potatoes), whole grains and a lot of greens.
Gagarina is also actively engaged in the gym, yoga and running.
